                     <interp inst="t18460921-1771-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 1 sovereign, 2 half sovereigns, 1 half-crown, 2 shillings, and 1 sixpence, the monies of <persName id="t18460921-name-115" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460921-name-115" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460921-name-115" type="surname" value="TAPPENDEN"></interp>
